_:Ne33d71e0c8f44677aa7bea30cbf1372c <http://schema.org/description> "DfT Operator Limited (DFTO) is the government’s public sector rail owning group. DFTO’s purpose is to bring all currently privately-owned train operators into public ownership in advance of the creation of Great British Railways in 2027. DFTO is a public corporation of the Department for Transport ." .
